,"format-standard","hentry","category-faith-iman","tag-agreed-upon-muttafaqun-alayhi","tag-exaltation-takbeer","tag-pilgrimage-hajj","tag-manners-adab","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-praise-hamd","tag-prophetic-biography-seerah-nabawiyya","tag-repentance-al-tawbah","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-travel-al-safr","tag-lesser-pilgrimage-umrah","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-42a","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":31722,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/02\/talbiyah-hajj-pilgrimage\/","url_meta":{"origin":15510,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Talbiyah: Responding to the call of Hajj pilgrimage","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 2, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would answer the call of the pilgrimage, saying, \u201cI am here at Your service, O Allah, at Your service! I am here at Your service, You have no partner! I am here at Your service! Verily,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18530,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/15\/hajj-umrah-cut-shave-head\/","url_meta":{"origin":15510,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Recommendation to shave head, permission to cut only","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: At the end of the Hajj pilgrimage, the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, have mercy upon those who shaved their heads.\u201d They said, \u201cAnd those who cut their hair short, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cO Allah,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14299,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/20\/hajj-umrah-together\/","url_meta":{"origin":15510,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Performing Hajj and Umrah together","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Subay ibn Ma\u2019bad reported: I raised my voice in preparation for both Umrah and Hajj together. Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYou have been guided to the Sunnah\u00a0of your Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1798 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15612,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/hajj-umrah-behalf-parents\/","url_meta":{"origin":15510,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Perform Hajj and &#8216;Umrah for parents","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Fadl reported: A woman from the tribe of Khath\u2019am said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, my father is an old man and Allah has obligated him to perform the Hajj pilgrimage, but he cannot ride on the back of a camel.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPerform\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23728,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/15\/pilgrims-guests-of-allah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15510,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Pilgrims are special guests of Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe pilgrims of Hajj and Umrah are the guests of Allah. He called them, and they answered him. They ask from Him, and He gives them.\u201d Source: Kashf al-Asta\u0304r 1075 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6568,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/hajj-umrah-rewarded-forgiveness\/","url_meta":{"origin":15510,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Umrah: Two pilgrimages rewarded with forgiveness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe 'Umrah pilgrimage to the following 'Umrah will expiate whatever sins were committed between them, and the blessed Hajj pilgrimage has no reward other than Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1773, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1349 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https: